WEBVTT

00:00:00.653 --> 00:00:04.106
.. ayere man gemakht in, ITALYA?

00:00:04.045 --> 00:00:09.163
nu, ⟨, ikh zog,⟩ er hot gefirt transpor- er hot gearbet, SHLIKHUT, vi azoy me zogt dos,

00:00:09.163 --> 00:00:11.143
sheliekh. er iz geven ongetun

00:00:11.217 --> 00:00:13.491
TSAVA kleyder,

00:00:13.491 --> 00:00:16.849
geven oyfgeshribn "P⟨O⟩LESTINE", "PALESTINE", ikh veys.

00:00:16.849 --> 00:00:20.474
SHLIKHUT er hot gearbet; er hot gefirt TRANSPORTIM.

00:00:20.211 --> 00:00:22.080
FÜR ⟨vem⟩ SHLIKHUT?

00:00:22.658 --> 00:00:24.289
 yidn,

00:00:24.413 --> 00:00:28.609
vos zey hobn gekumen in YISRA- vos zey hobn gevolt kumen in YISRAEL.

00:00:28.834 --> 00:00:31.747
hot er gefirt di transport fun,

00:00:31.820 --> 00:00:36.280
Estraykh oyf Italye. m'hot gedarft geyn tsu fus oykhet a sakh.

00:00:36.495 --> 00:00:38.683
er hot gef- -arbet SHLIKHUT.

00:00:38.892 --> 00:00:43.526
⟨un in,⟩, er hot gekrign legale ALIYA vayl er hot gearbet SHLIKHUT.

00:00:44.207 --> 00:00:45.163
KEN.

00:00:44.305 --> 00:00:46.361
un,

00:00:47.363 --> 00:00:48.622
vi lang

00:00:49.152 --> 00:00:51.373
hot ir im derkant

00:00:51.750 --> 00:00:56.520
az ir ho- biz ir hot zikh farheyrat? yo.

00:00:53.691 --> 00:00:57.347
f- gemakht di KHATUNA? a! zeyer shnel.

00:00:57.555 --> 00:00:59.456
zeyer shnel. ULAY

00:00:59.462 --> 00:01:01.042
a KHODESH, tsvey.

00:01:01.167 --> 00:01:04.755
yo. zayn bruder ⟨hot⟩ oykh dortn geh- geheyratet.

00:01:05.200 --> 00:01:12.110
ven ikh hob gemakht KHATUNA, iz geven nokh a KALA, a p- a p- fun POLANYA, a KALA.

00:01:12.110 --> 00:01:14.306
SHTEY KALOT, tsvey KALOT.

00:01:15.544 --> 00:01:18.373
un, yo.

00:01:19.037 --> 00:01:23.570
 un s'iz ge- s'iz gevezn a rov un a simkhe?

00:01:19.540 --> 00:01:20.540
UNK

00:01:22.345 --> 00:01:31.049
vi? nokh nisht geven rov demls. nokh di lager teykef, nisht geven rov. a frumer vo- a DATI vos er hot gekent,

00:01:31.049 --> 00:01:32.632
makhn KHATUNA.

00:01:33.550 --> 00:01:36.834
 zayn bruder iz gegangen in di shil.

00:01:36.840 --> 00:01:40.175
in ITALYA, in ROMA iz geven a KNESET,

00:01:40.384 --> 00:01:41.778
a BET HAKNESET.

00:01:41.886 --> 00:01:44.107
er hot geheyratet dortn.

00:01:45.953 --> 00:01:50.132
mayn man's bruder ⟨hobn⟩ geheyratet in BET HAKNESET BEROMA.

00:01:51.522 --> 00:01:55.690
undz, ikh hob nisht gevolt. far vos? ikh vel dir zogn far vos:

00:01:56.550 --> 00:01:59.069
di mentshn fun di

00:01:59.069 --> 00:02:04.740
kibuts ⟨hobn⟩ gedarft makhn LEHATS- gedarft makhn LEHATSBIA az me darf geyn in mikve.

00:02:04.740 --> 00:02:11.445
ikh hob mikh geshemt dos, BAKHURIM mit BAKHUROT zoln, makhn LEHATSBIA vegn mir, vegn mikve.

00:02:11.502 --> 00:02:16.434
ikh hob gezogt, "neyn. ikh'l heyratn in kibuts. ikh gey nisht, bay di

00:02:16.434 --> 00:02:18.228
BET HAKNESET UNK."

00:02:18.353 --> 00:02:21.010
un azoy iz geven. di andere...

00:02:19.669 --> 00:02:24.067
yo. un ir hot gehat a kleydl, a sheyn, a vaysn kleyd?

00:02:23.128 --> 00:02:24.843
a kurtse kleydl,

00:02:24.900 --> 00:02:26.767
a kur- nisht a lange.

00:02:27.921 --> 00:02:29.130
ikh hob gehat

00:02:29.220 --> 00:02:32.862
PTSAIM oyf di ponem. ikh hob gehat a infektsye oyf di ponem

00:02:32.862 --> 00:02:36.942
un ikh hob dos gekrign. ikh hob nisht gekent geyn makhn bilder oykh nisht.

00:02:37.624 --> 00:02:42.107
di bild vos ikh hob, dos iz gemakht fun a normale bild.

00:02:42.501 --> 00:02:45.785
gemakht ⟨a⟩ REGIL- ⟨a⟩ TMUNA REGILA,

00:02:45.842 --> 00:02:48.789
un a fotograf hot mir geleygt a shleyer,

00:02:49.909 --> 00:02:52.417
blumen, yo. me ken dos.

00:02:51.883 --> 00:02:53.429
yo..

00:02:53.267 --> 00:02:55.530
azoy. ober ikh hob

00:02:55.530 --> 00:02:59.049
nisht gevolt geyn, in mikve az ale

00:02:56.976 --> 00:02:57.976
⟨u-...⟩

00:02:59.173 --> 00:03:01.895
mentshn darfn LEHATSBIA vegn di mikve,

00:03:01.895 --> 00:03:05.917
vegn di bisele gelt vos me, darf kostn di mikve.

00:03:07.210 --> 00:03:08.280
⟨nu...⟩

00:03:07.324 --> 00:03:09.461
un, ir hot kinder?

00:03:09.602 --> 00:03:12.718
dray tekhter. ikh hob nisht gevizn di bilder?

00:03:12.252 --> 00:03:15.216
yo, yo. ikh vil, ir zolt dertseyln.

00:03:14.226 --> 00:03:17.790
y- a, yo! dray kinder hob ikh.

00:03:15.238 --> 00:03:16.396
yo.

00:03:17.027 --> 00:03:21.470
un, di ershte iz geboyrn...?.

00:03:19.643 --> 00:03:22.920
in ITALYA, in ROMA, in ROMA.

00:03:22.022 --> 00:03:23.501
vi heyst zi?

00:03:23.423 --> 00:03:28.108
BATYA, BATYA ⟨HOREN⟩. un DORI iz geboyrn do,

00:03:28.603 --> 00:03:30.144
un MIRYAM oykh do.

00:03:30.144 --> 00:03:33.693
MIRYAM hob ikh geboyrn mit a keyzershnit, di drite....

00:03:34.206 --> 00:03:38.220
keyzershnit, veystu vos...? yo, di drite.

00:03:38.357 --> 00:03:44.949
 un, ven zent ir gekumen in Erets-Yisroel?

00:03:44.938 --> 00:03:46.383
akht un fertsik.

00:03:46.204 --> 00:03:48.172
vi azoy hot ir gekumen?

00:03:48.145 --> 00:03:49.236
legal.

00:03:49.697 --> 00:03:51.665
legale ALIYA.

00:03:51.486 --> 00:03:52.728
mit a shif?

00:03:52.161 --> 00:03:53.572
yo. yo.

00:03:52.819 --> 00:03:54.348
UNK ir gedenkt?

00:03:54.253 --> 00:03:55.462
yo.

00:03:55.420 --> 00:03:56.420
vos?

00:03:55.620 --> 00:04:02.930
kh'gedenk zeyer gut, vayl di ershte nakht ⟨gesh- f- sh- f-⟩ -shlofn dortn bay di shif, azoy shlekht geven. kh'bin geven BEHERAYON shoyn mit di tsveyte.

00:04:02.930 --> 00:04:05.014
mayn man iz a gute mayster;

00:04:05.492 --> 00:04:08.624
ikh hob shoyn geshvang- ikh hob gehat a meydele fun tsvey yor,

00:04:08.715 --> 00:04:10.045
di groyse,

00:04:10.045 --> 00:04:14.661
un ikh hob shoyn geshvangert. ⟨un⟩ di shif, az me shvangert, iz zeyer shver,

00:04:14.661 --> 00:04:17.636
azoy sh-, nu, shlekht geven.

00:04:18.334 --> 00:04:21.790
ikh ⟨hob⟩ a gantse nakht, geven a shlekhte nakht.

00:04:22.350 --> 00:04:27.727
esn ikh hob nisht gekent, nor PASTASCIUTTA, nor di MAKARONIM hob ikh gekent esn. dort iz geven,

00:04:27.784 --> 00:04:35.237
 gemakht tishn, gel-... legale shif, m'hot ge⟨ge-⟩ -gebn gute esn dort, ober ikh hob nisht gekent,

00:04:35.530 --> 00:04:42.500
vayl ikh hob geshvangert mit di tsveyte, mit, DORIT. zi hey- zi voynt in KFAR SABA, DORIT.

00:04:42.820 --> 00:04:46.453
iz ikh hob nisht gekent esn. iz geven a shvere rayze.

00:04:46.453 --> 00:04:48.281
geforn tsen tog.

00:04:49.384 --> 00:04:53.107
tsen tog geforn mit di legale shif, yo.

00:04:52.720 --> 00:04:58.642
 un, z- dernokh, ven ir hot do gekumen tsum ⟨IS-⟩ Yisroel?

00:04:57.147 --> 00:05:00.094
a! ze'mir nisht geven in BET OLIM.

00:05:00.808 --> 00:05:03.564
zayne HORIM ⟨hobn⟩ do gevoynt in KIRYA,

00:05:03.564 --> 00:05:08.227
zayne IMA, ABA. mayn man hot gehat IMA, ABA. yo, gekumen nokh far undz.

00:05:05.432 --> 00:05:06.388
yo?

00:05:08.385 --> 00:05:09.222
KEN.

00:05:09.533 --> 00:05:15.810
iz, in SOKHNUT, m'hot gezogt, zol'mir voynen bay di IMA, ABA, vel'mir krign on a TOR di shtub.

00:05:15.810 --> 00:05:18.051
un azoy iz geven. ze'mir nisht geg-

00:05:18.051 --> 00:05:21.947
gegangen in ergets, nor gevoynt bay di IMA, ABA,

00:05:22.577 --> 00:05:28.007
un ven iz gevorn leydik di, eyn shtub... eyn tsimer, koydem gehat eyn tsimer.

00:05:28.007 --> 00:05:31.025
do iz geven BESH⟨UTFUT⟩; tsvey SHKHENIM ze'mir geven.

00:05:31.639 --> 00:05:37.151
iz, un azoy iz geblibn do di ale yorn. fuftsik yor ikh voyn shoyn do.

00:05:37.410 --> 00:05:42.146
KEN. do gekrign di shtub, un do geblibn. mayn man ⟨hot⟩ nisht gevolt avekgeyn.

00:05:43.097 --> 00:05:46.432
andere mentshn, avek, gekoyft sheyne shtiber,

00:05:46.489 --> 00:05:48.620
un er hot nor do gevolt.

00:05:48.936 --> 00:05:51.152
do hot er lib, vayl do hot er

00:05:51.152 --> 00:05:52.881
gem- beymer.

00:05:52.881 --> 00:05:57.670
er hot lib beymer, GINA; oto do

00:05:58.133 --> 00:06:00.060
hot er a basheftenung,

00:06:00.630 --> 00:06:02.092
un,...

00:06:00.664 --> 00:06:02.041
a SUKA.

00:06:02.520 --> 00:06:03.357
⟨MA⟩?

00:06:03.550 --> 00:06:07.560
vi zent ir, tsurik tsum lebn gekumen?

00:06:08.663 --> 00:06:10.676
ir kent undz ertseyln?

00:06:10.587 --> 00:06:11.931
tsum lebn?

00:06:11.785 --> 00:06:14.320
tsurik in gantse...

00:06:13.489 --> 00:06:15.913
nu, ven kh'hob shoyn gehat kinder...

00:06:18.282 --> 00:06:24.780
kh'hob gehat kinder, kh'hob nisht gekent geyn in ergets forn... a! kh'hob gemakht NITU-, operatsye in Italye,

00:06:24.998 --> 00:06:30.307
vayl ikh hob gevust, ikh kum aher, ikh hob nisht vu lozn kinder. ikh hob gevust, ikh vel nokh hobn kinder,

00:06:30.769 --> 00:06:32.923
 ikh blayb nisht mit eyn kind.

00:06:33.199 --> 00:06:40.247
ikh ⟨bin⟩ gegangen makhn dos. mayn man, di kind ⟨iz⟩ geblibn in kibuts, dortn geblibn.

00:06:40.759 --> 00:06:47.587
iz geven a yor, di ershte meydele iz geven a yor, ⟨un⟩ ikh ⟨bin⟩ avek in ROM- in ROMA. ikh hob gemakht NITUAKH do.

00:06:47.374 --> 00:06:48.751
vos iz dos?

00:06:48.657 --> 00:06:54.759
dos iz ⟨a SH-⟩ dos heyst a ⟨SH⟩TRUMA, ⟨SH⟩TRUMA. dos vakst aza shtikele vilde fleysh,

00:06:54.917 --> 00:07:00.716
un dos ⟨hob⟩ ikh gemakht NITUAKH. nokh, tsvontsik yor, ikh bin geven shoyn ongehoybn mit di NITUAKH.

00:07:01.077 --> 00:07:06.690
nokh dem hob ikh gemakht nokh NITUAKH: keyzershnit, geshnaydt, aroysgenemen di drite meydele.

00:07:07.489 --> 00:07:10.858
un ⟨v-,⟩ vos nokh? ikh hob nokh a NITUAKH...

00:07:11.067 --> 00:07:13.896
di REKHEM aroysgenemen. ikh hob gehat MIYOMA.

00:07:14.796 --> 00:07:17.990
di REKHEM. dray NITUKHIM ikh hob shoyn gehat.

00:07:18.930 --> 00:07:20.223
VEZEHU.

00:07:20.888 --> 00:07:25.387
un, dertseyl undz oyf ayere mey- kinder.

00:07:26.440 --> 00:07:28.577
a, mayne kinder?

00:07:29.967 --> 00:07:36.580
azoy. zey hobn, di tsveyte meydele hot gekhapt a bisele klep fun mayn man,

00:07:37.223 --> 00:07:42.470
geshlogn a bisele. zi iz geven a bisele ⟨a⟩ PRAIT. vi azoy zogt men? UNK

00:07:42.268 --> 00:07:43.330
vild?

00:07:43.011 --> 00:07:45.311
yo, a bisele PRAIT. er hot ge-

00:07:45.311 --> 00:07:48.725
gehat lib shlogn, ober ikh hob nisht geshlogn keyn mol kinder.

00:07:49.103 --> 00:07:51.139
keyn mol. AF PAAM.

00:07:52.478 --> 00:07:53.737
VEZEHU.

00:07:54.874 --> 00:08:01.250
a! di groyse hot gelernt. zi iz gegangen in TIKHON. zi hot gelernt alts GANENET,

00:08:01.371 --> 00:08:05.662
ober zi arbet nisht bay dos. in kibuts me arbet, yeder

00:08:05.662 --> 00:08:06.984
andere zakhn.

00:08:07.159 --> 00:08:11.160
zi hot gearbet in a KOLBO. veyst, in a kibuts iz do a KOLBO?

00:08:11.160 --> 00:08:13.080
yetst zi iz SADRANIT.

00:08:13.690 --> 00:08:15.945
un di mitlste

00:08:17.014 --> 00:08:25.682
hot oykh gearbet a sakh, ober ⟨z-⟩ nisht vayl zi hot gebroykht arbetn. ir man, iz, a MANKAL in di BANK LEUMI,

00:08:26.346 --> 00:08:27.723
iz a MANKAL.

00:08:28.202 --> 00:08:32.170
un di drite, zi hot gearbet MISKENA shver in a MOSHAV.

00:08:32.691 --> 00:08:34.660
host gehert EYN ⟨YAHAV⟩?

00:08:34.986 --> 00:08:36.988
EYN ⟨YAHAV⟩, in MOSHAV.

00:08:37.212 --> 00:08:40.429
zi voynt nokh dortn, ober zi hot nisht keyn MOSHAV.

00:08:40.690 --> 00:08:44.599
zi arbet alts, PKIDA in a BET ARIZA,

00:08:44.908 --> 00:08:47.551
zi arbet. un ir man arbet oykhet

00:08:48.115 --> 00:08:49.661
in TEL AVIV,

00:08:50.646 --> 00:08:53.857
in a fabrik, ikh veys vos, un,

00:08:53.857 --> 00:08:57.828
hot shoyn groyse kinder. di klenste tokhter hot shoyn oykh a KHAYAL.

00:08:58.341 --> 00:09:01.580
 un vifl eynikl hot ir?

00:09:01.007 --> 00:09:03.988
tsen. tsen eyniklekh, ⟨KEN⟩.

00:09:02.813 --> 00:09:04.427
un ureynikl?

00:09:04.551 --> 00:09:05.540
eyne.

00:09:05.817 --> 00:09:07.566
eyn ureynikl.

00:09:07.065 --> 00:09:12.750
 un, i-...

00:09:11.908 --> 00:09:15.243
host gezogt, kenst nisht yidish, ober du kenst yo gut!

00:09:16.617 --> 00:09:22.020
 ir hot ⟨a-⟩ ir hot aza,

00:09:22.310 --> 00:09:26.736
 shvere lebn gehat, biz ir hot do gekumen in Erets-Yisroel,

00:09:26.792 --> 00:09:28.203
un,

00:09:28.412 --> 00:09:31.528
es iz do epes az du vol- du vilst zogn,

00:09:32.243 --> 00:09:43.440
az du klerst, vos s'hot gevezn mit aykh un mit ayere familye, vos ir shpirt, un ir hot epes tsu zogn tsum kinder, tsum, tsu ale mentshn?

00:09:43.296 --> 00:09:48.858
ikh hob nisht vos tsu zogn. vos ken men, vos ken ikh zogn? kh'ken shoyn gornisht zogn.

00:09:51.143 --> 00:09:57.570
kh'veys, dos iz es. dos hot Hitler ongemakht, un azoy darf men onnemen far lib. vos ken men makhn?

00:09:58.450 --> 00:10:00.820
ken gornisht makhn ander min.

00:10:01.268 --> 00:10:03.742
me ken epes lernen fun dem?

00:10:06.690 --> 00:10:08.636
lernen? vos ken men lernen?

00:10:09.283 --> 00:10:12.939
di kinder mayne geyen, zenen geforn zen,

00:10:13.350 --> 00:10:17.100
di eyniklekh, zenen geforn in AUSCHWITZ un BIRKENAU⟨V⟩,

00:10:17.535 --> 00:10:20.786
⟨in⟩, dort in... BIRKENAU? UNK

00:10:20.877 --> 00:10:22.339
zen dortn.

00:10:23.526 --> 00:10:27.100
KEN. zey v- zey hobn lib tsu lernen ⟨oyf dos⟩...

00:10:25.686 --> 00:10:29.055
un, far vos hot ir gevolt dertseyln,

00:10:29.905 --> 00:10:32.295
far vos hot ir gevolt dertseyln

00:10:33.027 --> 00:10:35.282
ir, ayere SIPUR?

00:10:35.777 --> 00:10:43.640
a! ikh hob nisht gevolt., m'hot geshribn fun, kh'hob nisht ⟨ged-⟩ gedenkt az dos iz do aza min zakh.

00:10:43.827 --> 00:10:52.309
fun YAD VASHEM, m'hot geshikt epes a briv. mayn man hot gelezt dos... ikh gedenk afile nisht vos... un, zey hobn geshribn az s'iz do

00:10:53.226 --> 00:10:57.017
dos, me kumt aheym un me fregt ales.

00:10:57.158 --> 00:10:59.480
gezogt, "vos, vos ken ikh derleygn?

00:10:59.554 --> 00:11:02.248
vel ikh zogn. vos iz, a sod?"

00:11:02.389 --> 00:11:05.250
me, me veyst dokh yeder vos m'hot gelitn.

00:11:05.250 --> 00:11:07.060
⟨kh'hob gezogt, "BESEDER."⟩

00:11:05.983 --> 00:11:14.980
un i- un, ir, ir treft zikh mit andere mentshn, ir hot zikh getrofn, vos zenen gevezn in lager oder, ⟨⟩...?

00:11:13.662 --> 00:11:17.970
a! s'iz geven eyner, a alter mentsh,

00:11:17.970 --> 00:11:22.230
fleg ikh forn in HAIFA tsun im. er hot geredt HUNGARIT.

00:11:23.685 --> 00:11:31.829
KEN. nor BEEMTSA HADEREKH, ven er iz geforn HABAYTA... er iz oykh geforn oyf Budapest ⟨ven,⟩ ze'mir geforn ale HABAYTA,

00:11:32.089 --> 00:11:38.630
hob ikh gehert shtark kvitshen a mentsh. hob ikh nisht gevust UNK. vos iz geven? er hot getrofn a tokhter.

00:11:39.109 --> 00:11:43.541
di tokhter hot getrofn im. zi hot nisht gevust aza alter mentsh lebt nokh,

00:11:43.564 --> 00:11:49.312
iz geven a kvitsheray. hob ikh nokh dem gehert far vos zi hot gekvitshet, vayl zi hot getrofn dem ABA.

00:11:49.403 --> 00:11:55.320
er iz geven mit di zun bay undz in lager. der alter mentsh hot gehat oykh a BAKH- a zun,

00:11:55.326 --> 00:11:56.434
a BAKHUR.

00:11:56.845 --> 00:12:00.467
a ben hot er ⟨m-⟩ nisht aleyn iz er geven, oykh a ben, KEN.

00:12:00.642 --> 00:12:02.391
iz er geven mit im.

00:12:02.886 --> 00:12:06.052
zey hobn gemakht beyde SHI- LESHAKHRER.

00:12:06.244 --> 00:12:09.680
iz bay ⟨d- v-⟩ bay di zun, ikh bin nisht geforn keyn mol.

00:12:09.838 --> 00:12:11.992
kh'hob afile nisht gevust vu er voynt.

00:12:12.387 --> 00:12:14.068
nor bay di

00:12:15.002 --> 00:12:17.038
alte mentsh fleg ikh geyn.

00:12:15.745 --> 00:12:17.949
a, ir hot im ⟨br-⟩ bakent?

00:12:18.006 --> 00:12:23.110
ikh hob im gekent. nokh fun di lager ikh hob im gekent. KEN, BETAKH.

00:12:22.461 --> 00:12:24.227
un andere mentshn?

00:12:23.980 --> 00:12:28.040
LO, andere nisht. nor dem, nor dem hob ikh gekent.

00:12:24.537 --> 00:12:26.134
⟨,⟩ froyen?

00:12:28.418 --> 00:12:33.390
andere mentshn kh'hob gekent, ober zey, ale mentshn zenen gegangen voynen, ikh veys nisht vu AFILU.

00:12:33.784 --> 00:12:35.702
nor im hob ikh gevust.

00:12:35.809 --> 00:12:39.700
hob ikh gef- emetser hot mir gezogt zayne KTOVET,

00:12:39.775 --> 00:12:41.996
un azoy bin ikh gegangen bay im.

00:12:42.810 --> 00:12:45.456
biz ven ⟨er iz⟩ UNK ⟨gekumen⟩...

00:12:43.622 --> 00:12:47.986
ir gedenkt, gute mentshn vos hobn geholfn

00:12:48.769 --> 00:12:51.935
in lager, in, MAKHANOT,

00:12:52.366 --> 00:12:53.366
..

00:12:52.498 --> 00:12:54.618
vos ir kent dertseyln?

00:12:54.979 --> 00:13:00.592
LO. andere mentshn veys ikh nisht bikhlal, gute.

00:13:02.387 --> 00:13:04.760
un ir hot emetsn geholfn?

00:13:05.593 --> 00:13:10.734
vos hot men gekent helfn in di lager? m'hot nisht gehat gornisht. mit vos hot men gekent helfn?

00:13:10.875 --> 00:13:16.550
a! a mol, ven ikh hob gearbet, alts, SABALIT... ⟨S- vi azoy iz dos?⟩ SABALIT...

00:13:16.562 --> 00:13:19.576
fleg ikh geyn, hob ikh gebrengt kartofl

00:13:21.085 --> 00:13:28.140
un,... andere zakhn nisht. hob ikh arayngeleygt do a kartofl, tsvey, zol ikh emetsn kenen gebn. m'hot geleygt

00:13:28.140 --> 00:13:31.401
SENDVITSHIM oyf di broyt, azoy vi me leygt vursht.

00:13:31.401 --> 00:13:34.461
azoy hobn di mener nebekh gegesn azoy:

00:13:34.872 --> 00:13:36.654
kartofl geshnaydt,

00:13:36.863 --> 00:13:41.860
oyf di broyt geleygt. ot dos hob, ven kh'hob gekent hob ikh bahaltn

00:13:41.860 --> 00:13:45.670
⟨un ge⟩trogn far d- a mol dem man, a mol dem man geholfn.

00:13:45.670 --> 00:13:47.352
zey hobn gearbet nokh shverer.

00:13:48.152 --> 00:13:52.440
di mener hobn gearbet shverer nokh vi di froyen. BETAKH.

00:13:52.422 --> 00:13:55.010
 un ⟨d-⟩...

00:13:53.552 --> 00:13:55.710
azoy. epes andersh, neyn.

00:13:55.864 --> 00:14:02.237
eyn mol hob ikh geholfn... TOV, dos iz vayl ikh hob nisht lib gehat, NAKNIK fun, DAM,

00:14:02.395 --> 00:14:06.442
fun blut. ikh hob dos nisht gekent esn, vi hungerik ikh bin geven.

00:14:06.442 --> 00:14:12.940
ikh hob dos avekgegebn far, andere meydelekh, vos zey hobn geven mit mir in eyn, blok gevoynt,

00:14:12.940 --> 00:14:14.032
in eyn shtub.

00:14:14.393 --> 00:14:18.538
⟨ikh hob⟩ gegebn dos. ober ikh hob nisht gekrign a tsveyte zakh vegn dos.

00:14:18.882 --> 00:14:20.445
⟨ikh hob dos⟩ avekgegebn.

00:14:21.210 --> 00:14:22.937
du host shoyn gegesn a mol?

00:14:22.937 --> 00:14:25.558
UNK nisht yeder ken dos esn,

00:14:26.003 --> 00:14:28.191
NAKNIK fun DAM.

00:14:28.720 --> 00:14:31.701
⟨dos⟩. epes andersh ikh hob nisht gehat vos tsu helfn.

00:14:32.500 --> 00:14:34.215
vos hob ikh gekent helfn?

00:14:34.153 --> 00:14:40.050
un, ⟨do ir⟩, in Erets-Yisroel, ir zent, tsufridn?

00:14:40.617 --> 00:14:46.162
yo. nu, BETAKH. az m'iz gekumen aher darf men zayn tsufridn.

00:14:47.164 --> 00:14:51.630
koydem iz men tsufridn az m'hot sheyne meydelekh geboyrn.

00:14:52.277 --> 00:14:57.420
un, geven shvere tsaytn; er hot gearbet,

00:14:57.930 --> 00:15:02.710
oykh farshidene arbet. koydem iz, ven er iz arayn in KHEVRAT KHASHMAL, er iz geven sh-

00:15:02.710 --> 00:15:04.371
MISHTARA finef yor...

00:15:05.068 --> 00:15:12.600
MISHTARA? finef yor UNK BINYAN un andere pletser, nor dernokh dem iz er arayn in KHEVRAT KHASHMAL.

00:15:12.949 --> 00:15:16.605
ober azoy, ikh bin tsufridn. ale mol ikh bin a tsufridene.

00:15:16.628 --> 00:15:19.609
kh'vil ⟨nisht⟩ zayn a raykhe, kh'veys nisht vi raykh.

00:15:20.475 --> 00:15:24.910
⟨kh'bin⟩ tsufridn yetst oykh. di kinder kumen. KEN.

00:15:26.944 --> 00:15:27.944
⟨⟩.

00:15:27.057 --> 00:15:35.336
kumen yetst kumen zey nisht tsu fil, vayl ikh bin krank mit di fis; ikh ken nisht... a mol fleg ikh makhn ARUKHOT, zenen gekumen ale dray porlekh.

00:15:36.220 --> 00:15:41.890
ober haynt ikh ken shoyn nisht, tsugreytn ARUKHOT far zey. ⟨...⟩

00:15:43.611 --> 00:15:51.120
di tokhter fun KFAR SABA iz gekumen in kibuts, hot mir gemakht YOM HULEDET, SHIVIM.

00:15:51.475 --> 00:15:56.568
hot zi gebrengt fartike BASAR, gemakht oyf di ESH. in kibuts iz do

00:15:56.568 --> 00:15:58.606
MAKOM vegn tsu makhn dos.

00:15:58.680 --> 00:16:01.380
hot zi mir gemakht YOM HULEDET.

00:16:03.253 --> 00:16:08.420
nu, ikh hob keyn mol nisht geshlogn mayne meydelekh. mayn man hot a mol geshlogn.

00:16:09.075 --> 00:16:10.756
tor nisht shlogn kinder.

00:16:10.813 --> 00:16:13.880
du ⟨host⟩ geshlogn dayne kinder? ⟨oykh nisht?⟩

00:16:14.172 --> 00:16:15.803
⟨vifl⟩, eyn kind?

00:16:16.517 --> 00:16:18.097
a, du host dray?

00:16:18.407 --> 00:16:20.580
YOFI. ⟨LABRIUT⟩...

00:16:19.791 --> 00:16:20.645
AKHAR-KAKH.

00:16:20.580 --> 00:16:21.421
a.

00:16:21.770 --> 00:16:24.847
 un ir vilt undz tsaygn,

00:16:22.339 --> 00:16:23.058
⟨⟩.

00:16:24.760 --> 00:16:25.809
 vos?

00:16:24.988 --> 00:16:28.149
ir hot epes funem, bafrayt

00:16:28.149 --> 00:16:31.445
funem lager, ir vilt undz tsaygn? yo.

00:16:29.713 --> 00:16:33.830
nu, ikh hob dir gevizn, ikh hob a tsetl gehat, aha.

00:16:33.949 --> 00:16:36.271
ikh hob a tsetl fun TÜRKHEIM.

00:16:34.000 --> 00:16:38.027
 yo. ir vi- ir... BESEDER.

00:16:37.678 --> 00:16:39.545
yo, fun TÜRKHEIM.

00:16:38.438 --> 00:16:40.591
KEN. AZ,

00:16:41.138 --> 00:16:43.832
⟨BLI LEHAGID KLUM SHENARE⟩ TMUNOT? a.

00:16:44.192 --> 00:16:44.928
?

00:16:44.695 --> 00:16:46.734
ikh vil aykh gedenken

00:16:46.842 --> 00:16:47.713
nu?

00:16:47.500 --> 00:16:51.442
far dem intervyu. s'iz gevezn zeyer interesant.

00:16:49.272 --> 00:16:50.800
TODA RABA.

00:16:51.340 --> 00:16:52.910
yo, zeyer interesant.

00:16:52.663 --> 00:16:53.551
yo.

00:16:54.132 --> 00:16:56.303
un, ikh,

00:16:57.490 --> 00:17:01.888
ikh hof, ir zolt hobn langere yorn un zolt gezunt zayn.

00:16:57.523 --> 00:16:58.670
me darf k-...

00:17:01.607 --> 00:17:05.043
du oykhet. TODA RABA. du mit dayn mishpokhe.

00:17:05.269 --> 00:17:09.397
 me darf kumen nokh a mol shraybn?

00:17:09.723 --> 00:17:11.421
.. oykhet nisht.

00:17:14.078 --> 00:17:16.434
⟨ANI ROA HASHEM⟩?

00:17:16.496 --> 00:17:18.180
LO, TAGIDI...

00:17:17.502 --> 00:17:20.314
UNK vu bafrayt gevorn?

00:17:19.359 --> 00:17:22.275
yo. AZ, OD PAAM, UNK...

00:17:22.275 --> 00:17:24.550
dos iz der...

00:17:23.493 --> 00:17:27.622
⟨d⟩os iz in di bild, TMUNA SHIKHRUR,

00:17:29.805 --> 00:17:31.400
NEYAR SHIKHRUR.

00:17:32.550 --> 00:17:35.890
OD PAAM TAGIDI: ZOT TEUDAT SHIKHRUR.

00:17:35.762 --> 00:17:42.820
ZE TEUDAT SHIKHRUR MIMAKHANE RIKUZ VE-...

00:17:45.027 --> 00:17:50.522
ANI LO YODAAT MA LEHAGID OD PAAM. ZE HAYA BEMAY, SH⟨IKHRAR⟩TI BEMAY.

00:17:51.085 --> 00:17:52.564
BEMAY.

00:17:53.059 --> 00:17:55.922
⟨MI⟩TÜRKHEIM. TÜRKHEIM.

00:17:57.177 --> 00:18:01.423
ZE HAYA TMUNA BEKHATUNA ASITI.

00:18:03.100 --> 00:18:08.595
ANI VEBAALI ASINU ET HATMUNA HAZOT BAKHATUNA.

00:18:12.533 --> 00:18:19.290
ZE ANI VEBAALI BESHA- -SHANIM AKHRONOT ASITI.

00:18:20.937 --> 00:18:26.530
a! ZE TMUNA Z- BAKHATUNA SHEL HABAT SHELI HAYA.

00:18:26.530 --> 00:18:31.207
ZE AKH SHELI VEISHTO IM YELADIM SHELO VE-...

00:18:32.158 --> 00:18:36.120
HAYALDA SHELI AKHAT. YALDA AKHAT ZE SHELI.

00:18:36.546 --> 00:18:38.373
-AT SHELI... a!

00:18:38.373 --> 00:18:41.939
ZE BANOT SHELI IM SHALOSH YELADIM.

00:18:43.482 --> 00:18:47.596
⟨BEKHAT- ZE... L- LO HAYA... ZE...⟩

00:18:45.620 --> 00:18:48.300
OD PAAM: ZE HABAT HAGDOLA...

00:18:47.596 --> 00:18:49.635
KEN, ZE HABAT HAGDOLA

00:18:49.675 --> 00:18:52.369
IM SHALOSH YELADIM SHELA.

00:18:54.012 --> 00:18:55.960
.. BAALA, KEN?

00:18:55.380 --> 00:18:56.750
BAALA, KEN.

00:18:56.063 --> 00:18:57.063
KEN.

00:18:58.197 --> 00:18:59.569
HABAT SHELI

00:18:59.569 --> 00:19:02.797
VEBAALA IM SHALOSH YELADIM SHELA.

00:19:03.811 --> 00:19:05.630
HABAT HAEMTSAIT.

00:19:05.453 --> 00:19:07.438
a! HABAT HAEMTSAIT, KEN.

00:19:08.001 --> 00:19:12.551
ZE HABAT HAKTANA IM BAALA VEIM SHALOSH YELADIM.

00:19:13.317 --> 00:19:14.920
⟨YELADIM, KEN⟩.
